### About
Daily COVID19 dataset in Japan

- # of infected person per prefecture
- # of death per prefecture

### Period
2020/1/16-2022/2/15 (762 days)

### Notebook
[EDA Japan COVID-19 infection](https://www.kaggle.com/osamurai/eda-japan-covid-19-infection)

### Updating schedule
I will update datasets and maintain notebook if I feel like to do it. (Maybe once a month)

### Reference
https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/special/coronavirus/data/
